{"tid":1637886,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"奈良美智點石成金！大筆一揮 100蚊變45萬","createTime":"2019-10-08T06:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T08:41:41.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e3b07c9adbb1eee09fa48f9ad79b89e8ed93227","tid":1637886,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191008/large/1570510889_bd56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191008%2Flarge%2F1570510889_bd56.png&h=d621c80e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本月的香港秋拍，日本當代藝術大師奈良美智作品，不單一日內兩度破拍賣紀錄，其更點石成金，將一張原本面值100元港幣，變成價值45萬元的藝術品。<br />\n<br />\n蘇富比的香港秋季拍賣，昨日拍賣會上其中一件拍品，為一張經奈良美智「加工」的滙豐100元現鈔。有關作品最終落搥價36萬元，連佣金45萬元成交，升價4499倍。<br />\n另外，奈良美智之巨型裝置藝術《綠屋》，日前於保利香港拍賣會上，先以破紀錄4012萬元成交，至同日晚上蘇富比當代藝術晚拍，拍場上歷來尺幅最大的奈良美智畫布作品《背後藏刀》，以4,000萬元起拍，10分鐘後最終以破紀錄1.96億元（連佣金）成交；一日，內奈良美智拍賣紀錄急升近4倍，成為日本最貴藝術家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzWsKpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzWsKpu.jpg&h=86fe4561&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7576b282c3f8d20383c6a2016f72df987cce843f","tid":1637886,"uid":256330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:31:28.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"237ad79b2c4cb5c86d9b1a782c4dc38c715b2e33","tid":1637886,"uid":2974,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"奈良美智(坐監）"},{"pid":"9de5c1c7bfe0f1f6b3dcbaadd55fc50673a200a6","tid":1637886,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237ad79b2c4cb5c86d9b1a782c4dc38c715b2e33","tid":1637886,"uid":2974,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"奈良美智(坐監）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a477cf2f5d8dac7216551a0bd06503603106d793","tid":1637886,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":